859
00:42:47,088 --> 00:42:48,300
Play your card, Qian Fei.

860
00:42:58,060 --> 00:42:59,020
- Pass.
- Pass.

861
00:43:03,580 --> 00:43:04,620
- Pass.
- Pass.

